                    <h1 class="domdom">03</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/184">The War Game + Discussion (1965)</a></h1>

                    <h2>3 Feb 2008, 3 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Describing a 'limited' nuclear attack in Kent, this 1965 film is now widely recognised as an excellent piece of work, although it was kept off TV screens until 1985. Film followed by a discussion organised by Tyneside Medact.</p>

