                    <h1 class="domdom">19</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/209">Lord Of War (2005)</a></h1>

                    <h2>19 Oct 2008, 3 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Nicholas Cage plays the antiheroic protagonist, an illegal arms dealer with similarities to Russian arms dealers Viktor Bout and Leonid Minin. The film was officially endorsed by the human rights group Amnesty International for highlighting the trafficking of weapons by the international arms industry. 

</p>

