                    <h1 class="domdom">14</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/575">Waltz With Bashir (2008)</a></h1>

                    <h2>14 Mar 2010, 2 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Waltz with Bashir (Hebrew: ואלס עם באשיר‎ - Vals Im Bashir) is a 2008 Israeli animated documentary film written and directed by Ari Folman. It depicts Folman in search of his lost memories from the 1982 Lebanon War. To be followed by a talk with Miri Weingarten of Israeli Physicians for Human Rights.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/575">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

