                    <h1 class="domdom">10</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/667">Signs For Hope (2010)</a></h1>

                    <h2>10 Oct 2010, 2 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>A short film in which young people express their hopes for a future without nuclear weapons and war, and UK policy makers and disarmament experts talk about what is being done internationally, followed by a speaker from ICAN (International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear weapons).</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/667">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

